    <description>
Most of us don&#39;t have extensive musical training and would probably benefit from some tips on how to turn a hook, concept or a few loops into a song. 

Maybe you&#39;ve started a track and want to extend it into a full song format. But, how?  There&#39;s verses, bridges, chorus, refrains, etc.  What are the standard or common approaches for constructing a full song? 

@akabillposters - I&#39;ve noticed you commenting on song structure a few times and would value your input; Or anyone else with a knack for producing full tracks. Or perhaps you&#39;ve seen some good resources on the Net for explaining this stuff?</description>
    
